#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.gammainccinv.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.special.gammainccinv"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.gammainccinv:1 of
msgid "Inverse of the regularized upper incomplete gamma function."
msgstr "正则化上不完全伽马函数的反函数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.gammainccinv:3 of
msgid ""
"Given an input :math:`y` between 0 and 1, returns :math:`x` such that "
":math:`y = Q(a, x)`. Here :math:`Q` is the regularized upper incomplete "
"gamma function; see `gammaincc`. This is well-defined because the upper "
"incomplete gamma function is monotonic as can be seen from its definition"
" in [dlmf]_."
msgstr ""
"给定一个介于 0 和 1 之间的输入 :math:`y`，返回 :math:`x` 使得 :math:`y = "
"Q(a, x)`。这里的 :math:`Q` 是正则化上不完全伽马函数；参见 `gammaincc`。"
"这是良好定义的，因为上不完全伽马函数在其定义中是单调的，如 [dlmf]_ 中所示"
"。"

